**waigdt Privacy Policy**

waigdt does not collect, transmit, or share any personal data.
All data created by the extension which includes tasks, history, settings - is stored locally on your device using the browser's built-in storage API. This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to the developer or any third party.
The extension does not make any network requests, does not use analytics, and does not contain any tracking code.
